This file is about how to make the program work on your local machine.
You need to have tkinter install on your system for the purpose.
The date error needs to be corrected.
Then you need the two files prog1_copy.py and flight_order.txt
Using these 2 files you can run the entire program.
It will create mutiple files according to its needs.
The files are created using the source, destination and date.
The message boxes created during the flight booking are destroyed after 5 seconds timer.
We created a hash value for the name of the customer and used that hash value in all the 
respective files to provide some sense of security.
